            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Secession From Secession</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Mention of movement within the Southern states of people who support the
                    Union, and especially of a meeting in Alabama that passed resolves against their
                    state's secession. The article expresses the belief that these loyal Unionists
                    are the majority in the Southern states, and that they will eventually win out
                    over the secessionists.</summary>
